query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	bplusItSappiGetContacts (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		systemId
		systemName
		roleId
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	bplusItSappiFindContact (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		systemId
		systemName
		roleId
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)
{
	bplusItSappiFindContactById (id:$id)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		systemId
		systemName
		roleId
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:BplusItSappiUpdateContactInput!)
{
	bplusItSappiUpdateContact (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		systemId
		systemName
		roleId
		roleName
		name
		surname
		email
		mobile
		area
		hasConsentEmail
		hasConsentMobile
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)
